Package virusvoid.gui.other

package virusvoid.gui.other
  • Klassen
    Klasse
    Beschreibung
    GuiBasic
    The GuiBasic class is a JPanel extension providing basic GUI utility methods for creating transparent components, buttons, labels, and handling font-related tasks.
    GuiController
    The GuiController class manages the graphical user interface (GUI) components and handles the transition between different panels in the game.
    PlanetHPLabelManager
    The PlanetHPLabelManager class manages the display of the planet's health points (HP) label.
    SpaceshipKeyListener
    The SpaceshipKeyListener class implements a KeyListener for spaceship movement in the game.
    VolumeRegulatorBar
    Custom volume regulator bar component for setting music or sound effects volume.
